OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FA man from Sussex who attacked his dog
OL,7,Fhas been banned from keeping dogs for
OL,8,Ften years, following a prosecution by
OL,9,Fthe RSPCA.
OL,11,FAndrew Masters, 60, from St Leonards
OL,12,Fon Sea, appeared at Hastings
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court for sentencing
OL,14,Fearlier this month and pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto one animal welfare offence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
