OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FThe RSPCA said multiple concerns were
OL,7,Fraised by members of the public, who
OL,8,Freported that Masters had been
OL,9,Fverbally and physically abusive
OL,10,Ftowards his dog Rocco, a three-year-
OL,11,Fold bull-breed cross.
OL,13,FGeorgina Bowles, RSPCA Inspector, said
OL,14,Fvideo footage which had been recorded
OL,15,Fby members of the public, showed the
OL,16,Fdefendant displaying a number of
OL,17,Faggressive behaviours towards Rocco.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FIt included attempting to strike him,
OL,7,Fintimidating and shouting at him,
OL,8,F"using the lead to lift (Rocco) onto
OL,9,Fhis hind legs and hitting him on the
OL,10,Fnose", and a "forceful kick to
OL,11,F(Rocco's) face, seemingly unprovoked".
OL,13,FWhen he was presented with the
OL,14,Ffootage, the defendant described the
OL,15,Fphysical acts as "a tap on the nose"
OL,16,Fand "an accidental leg movement".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FThe animal welfare charity visited his
OL,7,Fhome on a number of occasions where
OL,8,Fthey said he was given "extensive
OL,9,Fadvice about neutering, positive
OL,10,Freinforcement training methods ... and
OL,11,Fadvised him to use a harness rather
OL,12,Fthan a collar".
OL,14,FThe defendant was also given advice by
OL,15,Fa number of different RSPCA Inspectors
OL,16,Fand Animal Rescue Officers about
OL,17,Fmuzzling.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FA vet, who also viewed the footage,
OL,7,Ftold the court: "(Masters) has
OL,8,Freceived a lot of advice through the
OL,9,Fpolice and RSPCA but still shows
OL,10,Faggressive verbal and physical
OL,11,Fbehaviour towards the dog. This
OL,12,Faggression has continued...
OL,14,F"The behaviour shown towards Rocco by
OL,15,F(Masters) is extreme aversive
OL,16,Fbehaviour and would not be advocated
OL,17,Fby any reasonable person...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,F"In (the videos provided to me) there
OL,7,Fare signs that the dog is frightened
OL,8,Fas shown by (him) cowering and putting
OL,9,Fhis ears back..."
OL,11,FIn November last year, the RSPCA, led
OL,12,Fby Inspector Andrew Kirby, alongside
OL,13,FHastings Police, attended Masters'
OL,14,Fhome, where they took Rocco into RSPCA
OL,15,Fcare.
OL,17,FAlongside the ten year ban from owning
OL,18,Fdogs, which he cannot appeal for five
OL,19,Fyears, Masters was also handed an 18-
OL,20,Fmonth conditional discharge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FHe was also ordered to pay #500 costs
OL,7,Fand a #26 victim surcharge.
OL,9,FIn mitigation, Masters said he had
OL,10,Fadopted the dog from a rescue centre,
OL,11,Fand had received differing advice on
OL,12,FRocco's care.
OL,14,FHe also mentioned that Rocco's
OL,15,Fbehaviour had been fine during the
OL,16,Ffirst six months of ownership.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
