OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776435067
OL,3,CSussex man banned from keeping dogs
OL,4,Cafter attacking his pet
OL,6,FHealth concerns, which affected his
OL,7,Fmobility and fitness, were also cited,
OL,8,Fand that he felt overwhelmed by
OL,9,Funsuccessful attempts to muzzle and
OL,10,Fput a harness on Rocco.
